"sadasator utpādāyogād" ityādinājātaṃ jagad yena buddhaṃ pratyakṣato jñātaṃ tasya prtītyasamutpannā buddhiḥ śuddhaiva bodhato nirvedhataḥ | atas tasya dhīmato 'nābhogenābhogaṃ vinaiva nijaṃ sahajaṃ jagat satyam avitatham ||

<commentary>adhunā vikalpo 'pi nirvāṇam iti darśayati—avibhāvitetyādi | avibhāvitasambandho 'viditasambandho 'sau vikalpaḥ prītyasamutpannaḥ | tat tasmād eṣa eva nirvāṇam iti | ataś citta bhrāntiṃ mā kuru | tad uktam—

	yaḥ pratītyasamutpādaḥ śūnyatā saiva te matā |

iti | śūnyatā ca nirvāṇam iti ||</commentary>

ajātajñānabodhena mahāmudrā yathā labhyate tad darśayati—pratipakṣa ityādi | pratipakṣa iti svabhāvaguṇasāranirūpaṇatayā dānaśīlakṣamāvīryadhyānaprajñātmakapratipakṣanirūpaṇavikalpāsaṅge 'manasikāreṇa varjanāt sthito naiva yaḥ | pratipakṣanirūpaṇavikalpāsaṅgaprahāṇyā sāsravarūpādipañcopādānaskandhādyātmakavipakṣanirūpaṇavikalpāsaṅgaprahāṇir api draṣṭavyā |
